    "storyId": "801071002",
    "title": "硝子の少女は遊びたい",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、購買部の雑貨コーナーで\nメジロアルダンを見かけた。",
            "enText": "One day, I saw a Mejiro Ardan in \nthe general merchandise section \nof the purchasing department.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 4242680254862911218
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -629524807384504402
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2358930112684895949,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "むぅ……トランプ、リバーシ……おはじき？\nもっと盛り上がりそうなものは……。",
            "enText": "Mmm… playing cards, reversi … playing cards? \nWhat could be more exciting…",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 7285154456923176806
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 3087629476979950958
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6174734978086331746,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "あら？　すみません。つい声に……。",
            "enText": "Oh? Sorry. I was just saying…",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -3236082426082693487
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 2386914436311182221
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3903578056119029445,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "あの……、突然で恐れ入りますが、\r\nなにかお部屋でできる面白い遊びって\nご存じありませんか？",
            "enText": "I'm sorry to bother you… but do \nyou know of any interesting games \nyou can play in your room?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "室内で遊べるもの限定？",
                    "enText": "Only for indoor play?",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 245895704500626789
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": -3317986742533772844
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2964442053180568889,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ええ、その……実は私、少し体が弱くて、\r\nそのせいでみなさん、外には誘いづらい\nようで……。",
            "enText": "Yeah, well… I'm a bit frail, actually, \nand that makes it hard for people \nto invite me out…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -1114865908889845453
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 8152691763767649398
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3838240080340870608,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "なので、なにか気兼ねしなくていい遊びに、\n私のほうからお誘いしたいのです。",
            "enText": "So I'd like to invite you to join me in some \nkind of fun where you don't have to worry \nabout anything.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": -246188370774172045
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 8991838591432217647
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6490796111124046260,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ですが……最近の遊びには詳しくなくて……。\nどういうものがいいのでしょう……？",
            "enText": "But I'm not familiar with… the latest games… \nWhat would you like to…?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "『かるた』なんてどう？",
                    "enText": "How about \"Karuta\"?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ウマトックに映え動画をアップとか？",
                    "enText": "Maybe upload a video of your \nreflection to Umatok?",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": -301682468354756111
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -2543820171373139112
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8234582573307907055,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "かるたですか……懐かしいですね。\n百人一首でしたら、昔よくやりました。",
            "enText": "Karuta… I miss it. I used to play \n\"Hyakunin Isshu\" a lot.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 4079408943041258149
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 4157651129918832481
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8096855188570810561,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "だけど、楽しんでもらえるでしょうか？\n最新の遊び、というわけではないですし……。",
            "enText": "But will you enjoy it? It's not \nexactly the latest game…",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": -7183471604824098359
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -7503993360205754906
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2526902342546816773,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふと商品棚を見ると、ユニークなかるたが\r\n置いてあったので、薦めてみた。",
            "enText": "When I looked at the product shelf, I saw a \nunique karuta, so I recommended it to her.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 7289308394063785099
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -3792281124585370618
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2997702095916277037,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "あら、それは？\n『激熱☆ウマ娘かるた』……？",
            "enText": "Oh, what's that? It's \"Uma Musume Karuta\"…?",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": 6577520020784785382
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -2608296117111257607
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3006505208717380060,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "『往年の名ウマ娘から現役ウマ娘まで網羅』？\nまぁ、こんなグッズが……！",
            "enText": "All the best Uma Musume from the past to the \npresent? Well, this is the kind of \nmerchandise you'll find…!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -2000572915784856850
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -2308398988653804519
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4579812293211649204,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "えーと、か、か、『か』は……。\n『笠松の　灰かぶり姫　オグリキャップ』",
            "enText": "Let's see, ka, ka, 'ka' is… \"Oguri-cap, the \nash-covered princess of Kasamatsu.\"",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -951402154255308433
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 5349501395434855827
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7301287062803890363,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "くすっ……！　うふふっ……！\nまぁまぁ、私の札もあるでしょうか？",
            "enText": "Sucks…! Mmmm…! Well, well, \nwell, do you have my tag?",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -7062281916128812707
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 4993971303625985568
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2148093351232068668,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "これなら楽しんでくれそう……！\n教えてくださってありがとうございます。",
            "enText": "I think they'd enjoy this…! Thank \nyou for letting me know.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 5058685248020144584
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 6547847903508782672
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 275798137615597570,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "今まであまり遊べなかった分、これで、\nみんなとたくさん思い出を作れたら……。",
            "enText": "I'm hoping that this will give me the chance \nto make lots of memories with everyone, as I \nhaven't been able to play much before…",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -7187470199483208914
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 6916359942536452046
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3164043233783152344,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう呟いて、彼女は微かに\r\n顔をほころばせたのだった――",
            "enText": "And then, with a slight smile \non her face, she said…",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 3163897357968097268
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -2521040267326676564
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3914913208788352501,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ウマトック……ですか。クラスの子から、\r\n名前だけでしたら聞いたことがあります……。",
            "enText": "Is it Umatok…? I've only heard the \nname from a girl in my class…",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": 6454263177130383792
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -2457726929219035763
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3445169050488432384,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "……あの、よかったら\n撮り方を教えていただけませんか……？",
            "enText": "… Um, I was wondering if you could \nshow me how to shoot…?",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -3238732917842887113
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 6581522248079102038
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3382882422554812839,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『ずきゅん♪　ばきゅんっ♪\nずずずずきゅ～～～～んっ♪』",
            "enText": "\"Zukun…\" \"Zukun…\" \"Zukun… ～～～～\"",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": -6959136808953500584
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": 7977626527830069078
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -981116799971420236,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ず……ずきゅん♪　ですっ！",
            "enText": "Z… is Zukun!",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2292579813115916010
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -7079248789182140946
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8609407463441697723,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "こんな感じですか……？\n少し恥ずかしいですね。",
            "enText": "Is it like this…? It's a bit embarrassing.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ちょっと編集するから待ってて",
                    "enText": "Just wait while I do some editing.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": -4060374492006285746
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -950689261388964574
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4341849864433743920,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "……うふふっ！　まぁすごい。\n最近はこんな素敵な遊びがあるのですね。",
            "enText": "… Woo hoo! Well, wow. This is such a \nwonderful game to play these days.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": -8347056876786656640
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": -5403453947669501710
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3717522307690776548,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "これならお部屋の中でも、\nみんなで楽しめそうです……！",
            "enText": "This is a great way to keep everyone \nentertained in your room…!",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -6677563379242779604
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": -2341589534144958465
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -6875558016673148383
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -70494567967300096,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女は楽しみな気持ちを抑えきれないかの\nように、にっこりと微笑んだのだった。",
            "enText": "She smiled, as if she couldn't \ncontain her excitement.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 7754840491780752675
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": -4382074423236150714
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -7627325072466126081
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7133835659533285723,
            "blockIdx": 25
        }
